<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA15">
<l>paṇintuyarnta pauvap paṭutiraikaṇ mōtap</l>
<l>paṇinta paṇamaṇika ḷālē – yaṇintaṅ</l>
<l>kaṉanta ṉaṇaikkiṭakku mammā ṉaṭiyēṉ</l>
<l>maṉanta ṉaṇaikkiṭakkum vantu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Lord, who rests on the bed of Aṉantaṉ,</l>
<l>as if adorned  with sapphires on [its] lowered hoods,</l>
<l>while the constant waves of the ocean, which lowers [and] rises, dash,</l>
<l>comes [and] rests on the bed of the mind of me, [his] servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
